data.description: If you enjoy nature then this Whispering Meadows 2 story will not dissappoint! Home backs up to beautiful open prairie. Plenty of room to spread out. Main floor features formal living room/dining room, kitchen with abundant cabinets and center island, all appliances, dinette area for kitchen table, family room with soaring ceiling,mud room, and main floor powder room. Upstairs you will find a generous size primary bedroom with walk in closet and private full bath,two other bedrooms, full bath, laundry room and loft overlooking family room. The finished basement has recreation room perfect for movie night, a dry kitchen/bar area and another full bath! Step outside to this unforgettable scenic yard overlooking a beautiful tall grass prairie. Paver patio with gazebo, gas firepit and pool built into a hillside. Fenced yard beautifully landscaped with mature flowering plants and shrubs. Home has all been freshly painted, new carpet throughout. Furnace and A/C about 10 years old. Truly move in ready!
